# Arcadia SDK

<p align="center">
  <!-- You could add a logo image here -->
  <h3 align="center">Deploy and Monetize ML Models with Ease</h3>
</p>

Arcadia is a powerful platform that enables machine learning developers to seamlessly deploy, manage, and monetize their models. With our SDK, you can transform your ML models into production-ready APIs in minutes.

## âœ¨ Features

- ðŸš€ **One-Click Deployment**: Deploy models to production with a single command
- ðŸ’° **Built-in Monetization**: Set pricing and start earning from your models instantly
- ðŸ“Š **Advanced Monitoring**: Track performance, usage metrics, and revenue in real-time
- ðŸ”’ **Enterprise-Grade Security**: SOC 2 compliant with end-to-end encryption
- ðŸ”„ **Version Control**: Manage multiple versions of your models effortlessly
- ðŸ“ˆ **Auto-scaling**: Handle varying loads with automatic scaling

## ðŸš€ Quick Start

### Installation

```bash
pip install arcadia-sdk
```

### Usage

```python
from arcadia import Model, predict

@predict
def my_model(input_data):
    # Your model logic here
    return prediction

Model("my-model").deploy()
```

